OL,3,CJersey bus company 'seriously
OL,4,Cconsiders' ending cash payments
OL,6,FHowever, the government's Economic and
OL,7,FInternational Affairs Scrutiny Panel
OL,8,Fare speaking to businesses to
OL,9,Funderstand whether they want cash
OL,10,Fprotected or continue to be naturally
OL,11,Fphased out of society.
OL,13,FIf Liberty Bus goes cashless, they
OL,14,Fwould follow in the footsteps of
OL,15,FGuernsey whose buses went cashless in
OL,16,FJuly 2021.
OL,18,FMr Hart said that while around 2.5% of
OL,19,Ftheir total sales are made in cash,
OL,20,Fthey only receive around 72p for every
OL,21,Fpound spent.
