OL,3,CJersey bus company 'seriously
OL,4,Cconsiders' ending cash payments
OL,6,FHe explained: "It's something we would
OL,7,Fneed to seriously consider when you
OL,8,Flook at the costs involved in handling
OL,9,Fcash.
OL,11,F"You've got the cost of the machines
OL,12,Fto count it, the individuals to bag it
OL,13,Fup, the security to collect the cash,
OL,14,Fthe bank charges as well, so there's a
OL,15,Fwhole process where the more cash we
OL,16,Ftake, the higher our costs."
OL,18,FThe Director reassured customers that
OL,19,FLiberty Bus is "quite happy" taking
OL,20,Fcash, but encouraged islanders to pay
OL,21,Fwith alternative methods.
