OL,3,CJersey bus company 'seriously
OL,4,Cconsiders' ending cash payments
OL,6,FThe prospect of Jersey phasing out
OL,7,Fcash payments has received pushback
OL,8,Ffrom some businesses and politicians.
OL,10,FIn June, Deputy Kirsten Morel told ITV
OL,11,FChannel that he would bring forward a
OL,12,Fproposal to protect cash payments on
OL,13,Fthe island.
OL,15,FHe explained: "It's my belief that we
OL,16,Fshouldn't lose cash and that's why I'm
OL,17,Fthinking of bringing a proposition to
OL,18,Fensure cash is maintained in Jersey.
